# Egress allow-list (extended regex vs the destination HOST). FilterDefaultDeny means ONLY hosts
# matching a line below are reachable — every line is a hole you opened. Do NOT add example.com:
# healthcheck.sh probes it as the host that MUST be refused; allow-listing it blinds the detector.
(^|\.)github\.com$
(^|\.)githubusercontent\.com$
# Package registries — drop the ones your project does not use.
(^|\.)npmjs\.org$
(^|\.)npmjs\.com$
(^|\.)pypi\.org$
(^|\.)pythonhosted\.org$
{{ALLOWED_HOSTS}}
